room_title: Escape room "Twisted" by New Smyrna Beach Escape Room in Daytona Beach
room_address: 116 Canal St New Smyrna Beach, FL 32168
room_description:
Twisted is a game of intense logic that will have you questioning everything you know to be a reality!
Not for those who are afraid of the dark or who panic at the thought of being trapped. Recommended for ages 16 and up but is open to all ages.
